## 🔍 Dry Run: `gain = [-5, 1, 5, 0, -7]`

| i | gain[i] | num (altitude)   | highest < num? | highest |
|---|---------|-------------------|-------------------|---------|
| — | —       | 0 (start)          | —                  | 0       |
| 0 | -5      | 0 + (-5) = -5      | -5 < 0? No         | 0       |
| 1 | 1       | -5 + 1 = -4        | -4 < 0? No         | 0       |
| 2 | 5       | -4 + 5 = 1         | 1 > 0? Yes         | **1**   |
| 3 | 0       | 1 + 0 = 1          | 1 > 1? No          | 1       |
| 4 | -7      | 1 + (-7) = -6      | -6 > 1? No         | 1       |

**Altitudes generated:** `[0, -5, -4, 1, 1, -6]`
**Final answer: `1`** ✅ matches expected output.

